Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer up to three floors of recently refurbished and creative office space in the heart of Surry Hills commercial and retail precinct.

Situated within 5 minutes of Central Station, 50 Cooper Street, Surry Hills offers efficient and single tenant floor plates with exclusive amenities and two sides of natural light.

Be spoilt for choice with a plethora of award winning cafes/bars/eateries at your doorstep (such as Porteno, Orto Trading Co, Dove and Olive, Sample Coffee, Café and Cucina & many more).

Key Features:

• 266sqm – 800sqm (available levels: Ground, 1 and 2)
• Polished concrete floors
• LED Lighting
• Fully air conditioned
• Flooded in natural light on each floor
• Exclusive kitchen and amenities on each floor – Male, Female and showers
• Either open plan or partially fitted offerings
• Operable windows allowing air flow through each floor
• Secure basement parking for 6 tenants plus visitor parking.  The premises is also in close proximity to parking stations within a few minutes’ walk
• Secure premises

Please get in touch with the agents below to organise an inspection or get further information:

Fergus Bowen

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: CREATIVE OFFICE/SHOWROOM OFFERING | MINUTES FROM CENTRAL

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Spread over two levels, this open plan, efficient 714sqm* property on leafy Foveaux Street delivers flexibility to an incoming tenant (or two). Situated 200 metres* from Central Station, you cannot find more convenient premises.

This property can be dressed up in a number of manners; with floor to ceiling glass, huge signage potential and street presence with plenty of foot and vehicular traffic, a showroom or retailer could utilise the ground floor as their shop/showroom, with head office upstairs.

Alternatively, a creative office user could utilise a single level, or take the whole space for a long term lease.  Situated in Surry Hills, with cafes/restaurants aplenty, give your business the best opportunity to succeed.

Previously occupied by AIM, 53-55 Foveaux Street has quality IT capabilities.

• Ground floor 364sqm*
• First level 350sqm*
• High ceilings with exposed services
• New air-conditioning and fresh paint
• Ready for reinvention

For more information, please contact the below agent.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Fitted out with boardroom and offices

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to present to the market for lease, Level 2 at 63 Foveaux Street Surry Hills.

63 Foveaux Street is a creative tenants dream, with a well maintained an efficient fit out in a building located moments from Central Station.  Foveaux Street is loaded with cafes, bars, restaurants & eateries – your staff will never have to stink out the office with their microwaved leftovers again!

Level 2 has a northern facing aspect, with big windows fronting both the North and South of the building.

The floor features:

- 321sqm* whole floor offering
- Fitted board room and two offices / meeting rooms
- Large kitchen/breakout
- Ducted Air Conditioning throughout
- High speed internet connectivity
- Polished timber flooring
- Secure swipe access
- 1 car space at an additional price
